sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.040ftth)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.040ftth ns:medicine.medical_trial_design.trials ?y .
?y ns:medicine.medical_trial.references ?x .
?x ns:book.written_work.author ns:m.04mkn76 .
?y ns:medicine.medical_trial.eligibility_exclusion_criteria ?sk0 .
}
ORDER BY xsd:datetime(?sk0)
LIMIT 1
